## Connection Alert

<insight>
Pronouns = Cases in Action!

**Accusative** (με, σε, τον) answers "WHOM/WHAT do I [verb]?"
**Genitive** (μου, σου, του) answers "WHOSE?"

You're already using cases every time you use a pronoun!
</insight>

