## Double Object Pattern

<pattern name="double-object">
<title>"Give me it" word order</title>
<explanation>Greek puts the person before the thing</explanation>

| English          | Greek       | Literal        |
|------------------|-------------|----------------|
| give it to me    | δώσε μου το | give to-me it  |
| tell it to me    | πες μου το  | tell to-me it  |
| bring it to her  | φέρε της το | bring to-her it|

</pattern>

